thread.title: Kendra

author: Kendra
title: Kendra
text: This company did a great job at responding quickly when receiving my book and was also quick to send out the check in the mail to pay me for the book. They also stayed in touch with me about every detail in between so that I felt safe going through them to sell my books. Thank you Cash 4 Books for making this process so easy! I will definitely sell to you again in the future!
